---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Overview" description="Welcome to FruitFly documentation. Learn how to use the bug tracking API and CLI.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">
      Welcome to FruitFly
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed">
      A self-hosted bug and feature request tracking system with a powerful REST API and CLI.
      Built for developer teams who value speed and simplicity.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Quick links cards -->
  <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-12">
    <a href="/docs/quickstart/" class="group p-5 rounded-sm border border-base-300/50 bg-base-200/30 hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors">
      <div class="size-9 rounded-sm bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:glow-primary transition-shadow">
        <svg class="size-4 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm text-base-content mb-1">Quick Start</h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted">Get up and running in minutes with Docker</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/docs/authentication/" class="group p-5 rounded-sm border border-base-300/50 bg-base-200/30 hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors">
      <div class="size-9 rounded-sm bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:glow-primary transition-shadow">
        <svg class="size-4 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 7a2 2 0 012 2m4 0a6 6 0 01-7.743 5.743L11 17H9v2H7v2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2.586a1 1 0 01.293-.707l5.964-5.964A6 6 0 1121 9z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm text-base-content mb-1">API Keys</h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted">Learn about authentication and API key types</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/docs/api/issues/" class="group p-5 rounded-sm border border-base-300/50 bg-base-200/30 hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors">
      <div class="size-9 rounded-sm bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:glow-primary transition-shadow">
        <svg class="size-4 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm text-base-content mb-1">Issues API</h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted">Create, list, and manage issues via REST API</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/docs/cli/" class="group p-5 rounded-sm border border-base-300/50 bg-base-200/30 hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors">
      <div class="size-9 rounded-sm bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:glow-primary transition-shadow">
        <svg class="size-4 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm text-base-content mb-1">CLI Tool</h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted">Manage issues from your terminal</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Core concepts -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">Core Concepts</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm max-w-none">
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        FruitFly is organized around a few key concepts:
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-sm border border-base-300/50 bg-base-200/20">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-primary font-medium mt-0.5">Accounts</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">
            Multi-tenant containers that isolate projects and issues. Each account has its own users, projects, and API keys.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-4 rounded-sm border border-base-300/50 bg-base-200/20">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-primary font-medium mt-0.5">Projects</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">
            Containers for organizing issues. Each project has a unique prefix used in issue keys (e.g., <code class="text-primary">FF-123</code>).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-4 rounded-sm border border-base-300/50 bg-base-200/20">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-primary font-medium mt-0.5">Issues</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">
            Bug reports or feature requests with status, priority, and type. Issues belong to a project and have human-readable keys.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-4 rounded-sm border border-base-300/50 bg-base-200/20">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-primary font-medium mt-0.5">API Keys</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">
            Authentication credentials scoped to an account. <code class="text-primary">pk_*</code> keys are read-only, <code class="text-primary">sk_*</code> keys have full access.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Next steps -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">Next Steps</h2>
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <a href="/docs/quickstart/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">
        <svg class="size-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
        Deploy FruitFly with Docker
      </a>
      <a href="/docs/authentication/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">
        <svg class="size-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
        Set up API authentication
      </a>
      <a href="/docs/api/issues/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">
        <svg class="size-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
        Explore the Issues API
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
